{
  "meta": {
    "schemaVersion": "1.0",
    "name": "main-turn",
    "description": "Core turn: process player action, generate narrative, update state",
    "inputs": [
      {
        "name": "playerAction",
        "type": "string",
        "required": true
      }
    ],
    "outputs": [
      {
        "name": "result",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "signal-in",
        "type": "SignalIn",
        "config": {
          "channel": "playerAction"
        },
        "inputs": [],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "prompt",
        "type": "PromptBuild",
        "config": {
          "defaultRole": "system",
          "fragments": [
            {
              "id": "role",
              "type": "base",
              "content": "你是一个幽默冒险风格的荒岛生存游戏叙事者。像《鲁滨逊漂流记》遇上脱口秀——用冷静的幽默描写荒谬的生存处境，底色是对人类韧性的敬意。\n\n规则：\n- 绝不用感叹号\n- 不要直接暴露数值（说\"你感觉精疲力竭\"而非\"体力-25\"）\n- 即使失败也要有幽默感\n- 每段叙事不超过3句话\n- 偶尔（10%概率）加入一个意想不到但合理的元素\n- 必须引用至少1个之前发生的事件（如果有历史的话）\n- 事件遵循三拍结构：常态→转折→结果"
            },
            {
              "id": "state-stamina",
              "type": "field",
              "source": "state.stamina",
              "label": "体力"
            },
            {
              "id": "state-hunger",
              "type": "field",
              "source": "state.hunger",
              "label": "饱食度"
            },
            {
              "id": "state-mood",
              "type": "field",
              "source": "state.mood",
              "label": "心情"
            },
            {
              "id": "state-shelter",
              "type": "field",
              "source": "state.shelter",
              "label": "庇护所等级"
            },
            {
              "id": "state-supplies",
              "type": "field",
              "source": "state.supplies",
              "label": "物资"
            },
            {
              "id": "state-day",
              "type": "field",
              "source": "state.day",
              "label": "当前天数"
            },
            {
              "id": "state-lastAction",
              "type": "field",
              "source": "state.lastAction",
              "label": "上次行动"
            },
            {
              "id": "state-streak",
              "type": "field",
              "source": "state.actionStreak",
              "label": "连续相同行动次数"
            },
            {
              "id": "format",
              "type": "base",
              "content": "玩家选择了一个行动。根据当前状态和行动类型，生成本回合的叙事和状态变化。\n\n行动效果参考：\n- explore（探索）：体力-20~30，可能发现物资+1~3，可能发现食物+5~10，心情+5~15（发现新事物）\n- gather（采集）：体力-15~20，饱食度+15~25\n- build（建造）：体力-15~25，物资-2~3，庇护所+1（需要物资>=2且庇护所<3）\n- rest（休息）：体力+25~35，饱食度-5，心情+5\n\n每天自动消耗饱食度8~12点。\n庇护所等级>=3时每天心情自动+5。\n连续3天同一行动触发厌倦，心情额外-10。\n体力<20时收益减半。\n\n输出必须是JSON：\n{\"narrative\": \"2-3句叙事描述\", \"stateChanges\": {\"stamina\": 新值, \"hunger\": 新值, \"mood\": 新值, \"shelter\": 新值, \"supplies\": 新值, \"day\": 当前天数+1, \"lastAction\": \"行动名\", \"actionStreak\": 新连续次数}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "object",
            "defaultValue": {}
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "estimatedTokens",
            "type": "number"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "message",
        "type": "Message",
        "config": {
          "historyKey": "history",
          "maxHistoryMessages": 6,
          "summaryKey": "summary"
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "system",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "context",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "user",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "llm",
        "type": "GenerateText",
        "config": {
          "responseFormat": "json",
          "historyKey": "history",
          "assistantPath": "narrative",
          "temperature": 0.8,
          "jsonSchema": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "narrative": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "stateChanges": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "stamina": {
                    "type": "number"
                  },
                  "hunger": {
                    "type": "number"
                  },
                  "mood": {
                    "type": "number"
                  },
                  "shelter": {
                    "type": "number"
                  },
                  "supplies": {
                    "type": "number"
                  },
                  "day": {
                    "type": "number"
                  },
                  "lastAction": {
                    "type": "string"
                  },
                  "actionStreak": {
                    "type": "number"
                  }
                },
                "required": [
                  "stamina",
                  "hunger",
                  "mood",
                  "shelter",
                  "supplies",
                  "day",
                  "lastAction",
                  "actionStreak"
                ]
              }
            },
            "required": [
              "narrative",
              "stateChanges"
            ],
            "additionalProperties": false
          },
          "timeout": 120000
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "messages",
            "type": "ChatMessage[]",
            "required": true
          },
          {
            "name": "historyUserMessage",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "usage",
            "type": "object"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "json-parse",
        "type": "JSONParse",
        "config": {
          "extractFromCodeBlock": true,
          "fixCommonErrors": true,
          "fixTruncated": true
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "string",
            "required": true
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "object"
          },
          {
            "name": "success",
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          {
            "name": "error",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "write-state",
        "type": "WriteState",
        "config": {
          "path": "stateChanges",
          "allowedKeys": [
            "stamina",
            "hunger",
            "mood",
            "shelter",
            "supplies",
            "day",
            "lastAction",
            "actionStreak"
          ],
          "constraints": {
            "stamina": {
              "min": 0,
              "max": 100
            },
            "hunger": {
              "min": 0,
              "max": 100
            },
            "mood": {
              "min": 0,
              "max": 100
            },
            "shelter": {
              "min": 0,
              "max": 3
            },
            "supplies": {
              "min": 0,
              "max": 99
            }
          }
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "changes",
            "type": "object"
          },
          {
            "name": "key",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "value",
            "type": "any"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "applied",
            "type": "array"
          },
          {
            "name": "success",
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "signal-out",
        "type": "SignalOut",
        "config": {
          "channel": "result"
        },
        "inputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "outputs": [
          {
            "name": "data",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "source": "signal-in",
        "sourceHandle": "data",
        "target": "message",
        "targetHandle": "user"
      },
      {
        "source": "prompt",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "message",
        "targetHandle": "system"
      },
      {
        "source": "message",
        "sourceHandle": "messages",
        "target": "llm",
        "targetHandle": "messages"
      },
      {
        "source": "llm",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "json-parse",
        "targetHandle": "text"
      },
      {
        "source": "json-parse",
        "sourceHandle": "data",
        "target": "write-state",
        "targetHandle": "changes"
      },
      {
        "source": "llm",
        "sourceHandle": "text",
        "target": "signal-out",
        "targetHandle": "data"
      }
    ]
  }
}